=head1 DESCRIPTION

For use with DVB-DASH profiles only. The settings for error reporting
from the playback device that you want Elemental MediaPackage to pass
through to the manifest.

=head1 ATTRIBUTES


=head2 Probability => Int

The number of playback devices per 1000 that will send error reports to
the reporting URL. This represents the probability that a playback
device will be a reporting player for this session.


=head2 B<REQUIRED> ReportingUrl => Str

The URL where playback devices send error reports.



